These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-1::.
There 3 different types of food: cauliflower, pineapple, pomegranate
The people have 3 different hobbies: fishing, card-games, singing
1. the person eating cauliflower is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is singing##3
3. the person who's hobby is fishing is the person eating pineapple##1
4. the person eating pomegranate is on the far left##1
5. the person who's hobby is card-games is the person who's hobby is card-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| Food   | pomegranate | cauliflower | pineapple |
| Hobby    | card-games    | singing | fishing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, drawing, filmmaking
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, blend, game
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the far right##1
2. the blend-smoker is in an even position##4
3. the game-smoker is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
4. the blend-smoker is the blend-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Hobby       | drawing | filmmaking | board-games |
| Cigar   | game    | blend     | oliveros        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-3::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: subway, tram, motorbike
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: dubstep, electronic, salsa
1. the person driving the subway is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1
2. the fan of electronic is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
3. the person driving the tram is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3    |
| Transport         | motorbike     | tram | subway |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | dubstep     | salsa  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-4::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, paramedic, project-manager
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: biathlon, cricket, lacrosse
1. the paramedic is the person who's sport is cricket##1
2. the accountant is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
3. the paramedic is in an even position##4
4. the paramedic is on the right of the project-manager##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |
| Job   | project-manager | paramedic  | accountant  |
| Sport         | biathlon  | cricket | lacrosse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-5::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: camping, chess, gardening
City: edinburgh, liverpool, nizza
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is between the person who's hobby is camping and the person traveling to edinburgh##2
2. the person who's hobby is chess is in an odd position##4
3. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3     |
| Hobby         | camping   | gardening | chess    |
| City   | liverpool | nizza     | edinburgh |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-6::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: zombie, romance, disaster
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cricket, lacrosse, tennis
1. the person watching zombie movies is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
2. the person who's sport is tennis is the person watching romance movies##1
3. the person watching romance movies is in an odd position##4
4. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Movie-Genre   | romance | disaster | zombie   |
| Sport   | tennis     | cricket    | lacrosse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-7::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: documentary, horror, martial-arts
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: poppy, iris, rose
1. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
2. the person watching documentary movies is between the person who growsrose and the person watching martial-arts movies##2
3. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
4. the person who growspoppy is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |   3    |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | documentary | horror |
| Flower           | iris         | poppy         | rose |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-8::.
There 3 different types of food: artichoke, carrot, kale
3 different games are played: canasta, whist, go
1. the person playing canasta is between the person playing whist and the person eating artichoke##2
2. the person playing go is in an odd position##4
3. the person playing whist is on the left of the person eating kale##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |  2   |     3     |
| Food   | carrot | kale | artichoke |
| Game    | whist    | canasta | go     |

