.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, coffee, cola
House: futuristic, victorian, ranch-style
1. the futuristic house is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
2. the ranch-style house is in an even position##4
3. the ranch-style house is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Beverage   | 7up    | cola      | coffee |
| House       | victorian | ranch-style | futuristic   |

