.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-11::.
There 3 different types of food: eggplant, watermelon, pepper
The people use 3 different means of transport: helicopter, subway, trike
1. the person eating pepper is on the right of the person eating watermelon##1
2. the person driving the helicopter is the person eating eggplant##1
3. the person driving the trike is the person eating pepper##1
4. the person eating pepper is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2    |     3      |
| Food         | watermelon | pepper | eggplant |
| Transport   | subway | trike   | helicopter |

