.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-12::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: poppy, azalea, daffodil
The people use 3 different means of transport: scooter, taxi, van
1. the person driving the van is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
2. the person who growspoppy is the person driving the van##1
3. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the person who growsazalea##3
4. the person driving the van is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |
| Flower   | daffodil | azalea | poppy |
| Transport     | taxi     | scooter   | van        |

