.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-13::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, cain, montecristo
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cycling, sailing, tennis
1. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the montecristo-smoker##1
2. the person who's sport is cycling is the cain-smoker##1
3. the montecristo-smoker is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
