2. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
3. the fan of hip-hop is on the left or right of the person playing backgammon##3
4. the person playing backgammon is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |
| Game   | whist  | backgammon     | domino |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop | ambient | jazz    |

