.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-20::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: aquamarine, amber, grey
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: golf, handball, lacrosse
1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who likes grey##1
3. the person who likes grey is in an even position##4
4. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person who likes amber##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |     3      |
| Color     | amber  | grey   | aquamarine |
| Sport   | lacrosse | handball | golf       |

 